{"tid":1474028,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[818] 我在十八日早晨，才知道上午有群眾向執政府請願的事","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T13:38:40.000Z","uid":152630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"066cde75aad90e42efdbac34126f3b4113e78da9","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"我在十八日早晨，才知道上午有群眾向執政府請願的事；下午便得到噩耗，說衛隊居然開槍，死傷至數百人，而劉和珍君即在遇害者之列。 但我對於這些傳說，竟至於頗為懷疑。 我向來是不憚以最壞的惡意，來推測中國人的，然而我還不料，也不信竟會下劣兇殘到這地步。 況且始終微笑著的和藹的劉和珍君，更何至於無端在府門前喋血呢？<br />\n 然而即日證明是事實了，作證的便是她自己的屍骸。 還有一具，是楊德群君的。 而且又證明著這不但是殺害，簡直是虐殺，因為身體上還有棍棒的傷痕。<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但段政府就有令，說她們是&ldquo;暴徒&rdquo;！</span></span></strong><br />\n 但<span style=\"color: red;\">接著就有流言，說她們是受人利用的。</span><br />\n 慘象，已使我目不忍視了；流言，尤使我耳不忍聞。 我還有什麼話可說呢？ <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我懂得衰亡民族之所以默無聲息的緣由了。 沉默呵，沉默呵！ 不在沉默中爆發，就在沉默中滅亡。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">八一八見！光復香港！時代革命！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a202a398b0c636b8c1a79ca58befe1baf5685e81","tid":1474028,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:42:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>8月15日</strong>：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b06ab930d98a7b1a9894d5fa0338c7120c1a2f66","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:54:26.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"9817add6efd9e3bdae765a374b768c32706301f2","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"7261ca5296f7ee12f3f1df76185f1d231b31b499","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"17772076fb22bc1af84419b6d4656e710c1e35d3","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"c562b687f598c22f054763f328d8e3b5d6d588b8","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"d7416167f23cf91f95305e9df2ec222b23c53b54","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:43:57.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"e424084eed8be8042286bac8bf724c827020ac5a","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:14:04.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"aad3775decfcbc1f0c8008c8fe045a5f7e770adc","tid":1474028,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"818"}]}